  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t上海前几天的万圣节活动，街头上民众们各种花式玩梗嘲讽维尼和中共统治下的社会乱象，最后出动狗腿子警察强行封路封地铁，驱散民众。维尼在墙内算是民心尽失，只能靠花钱豢养的五毛网军挽尊。墙国民众不是没有反抗心，而是中共之前的维稳掩盖了暗流涌动<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2M5YzBkZmE5NDE5NWFiNDc4YWQ0LmpwZz93aWR0aD02NjEmaGVpZ2h0PTkwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc9c0dfa94195ab478ad4.jpg?width=661&amp;height=900\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc9c0dfa94195ab478ad4.jpg?width=661&amp;height=900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cc9c0dfa94195ab478ad4.jpg?width=661&amp;height=900\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDUwZDU1ZmMzNTFiZTYyZGM4YTJlLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0xNDQw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d50d55fc351be62dc8a2e.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1440\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d50d55fc351be62dc8a2e.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1440\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d50d55fc351be62dc8a2e.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=1440\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNjdkZjViODcxYzhhZjdiMDQ4YTY2LmpwZz93aWR0aD05MDYmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMzE\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/67df5b871c8af7b048a66.jpg?width=906&amp;height=1231\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/67df5b871c8af7b048a66.jpg?width=906&amp;height=1231\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/67df5b871c8af7b048a66.jpg?width=906&amp;height=1231\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNDMzMzc1MTAxMTM5OWZjNmJkOTc0LmpwZz93aWR0aD02NTEmaGVpZ2h0PTEwNDU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4333751011399fc6bd974.jpg?width=651&amp;height=1045\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4